<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>You're Invited to <%= orgName %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f6f8fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Welcome to <%= orgName %>!</h2>
    </div>

    <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

    <p>You’ve been invited to join <strong><%= orgName %></strong>. This organization uses our platform to manage their team and tools, and you’ve been selected to be a part of it.</p>

    <p>Click the button below to accept the invitation and get started:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= url %>" class="button">Join <%= orgName %></a>
    </div>

    <p>If you were not expecting this email, you can safely ignore it.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= orgName %>. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
